  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->  
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this warm-up is to elicit the idea that there are different quantities of toppings on each pizza, which will be useful when students create pizzas with given numbers of toppings in a later activity. While students may notice and wonder many things about these images, the number of toppings is the important discussion point. Students use more, fewer, and the same as to describe the quantities they see.</p>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Materiales requeridos de la actividad -->
  <!-- <paragraphs> -->
